(44, 'THE PRICE INCLUDES ', 'Accommodation in 3*** hotels (local standards) and in homestay accommodation as scheduled in the program -\r\nThe meals mentioned as « included » in the program -\r\nPrivate and collective ground transports -\r\nEnglish speaking assitance at airports and stations as scheduled in the program -\r\nReturn trip ticket train to / from Aguas Calientes  - \r\nReturn trip tickets for the shuttle bus to / from Machu Picchu site -\r\nTouristic bus Cusco-Puno with an Engligh speaking guide on board -\r\nLocal English speaking guides for the excursions mentioned in the program -\r\nExcursions scheduled in the program -\r\nEntrances to the sites scheduled in the program-\r\nDomestic flights Lima – Cusco and Juliaca – Lima ', 75, '2017-10-10 10:26:57', '2017-10-10 10:26:57'),
(45, 'THE PRICE DOES NOT INCLUDE', '•	International flights \r\n•	Insurance\r\n•	Entrance to the thermal baths of Chivay (4 USD / person)\r\n•	Lunches and dinners not mentioned in the program (expect 5 to 10 USD per meal)\r\n•	Drinks\r\n•	Tips (2USD / day / person for the guide and 1USD / day / person for the carriers, mule-drivers, cooks)\r\nThe single supplement, please ask us. ', 75, '2017-10-10 10:26:57', '2017-10-10 10:26:57'),
